                },
                "p": [
                    {
                        "value": "The Bernard R. Danchik Collection was donated to the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives in October 1983 by Danchik's wife, Lili Danchik LaRocque. This collection came to New York University in January 2001 as part of the original acquisition of ALBA collections, formerly housed at Brandeis University."
